{"tid":962432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】北海道凌晨5.4級地震","createTime":"2018-12-31T00:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T00:33:53.000Z","uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21e08ac71fdd305d11e812d93a9d4fc366c3c63b","tid":962432,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181230/s00005/dc196754a8020893642dc2dabf9dae78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181230%2Fs00005%2Fdc196754a8020893642dc2dabf9dae78.jpg&h=d6be4753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - 震央（紅叉示）位於十勝地方南部，釧路西南約120公里。（日本氣象廳）<br />\n<br />\n繼暴雪後，日本北海道再受天災侵襲。日本氣象廳表示，本港時間今日凌晨3時左右，北海道南部發生5.4級地震。據報，震央位於十勝地方南部，釧路西南約120公里，震源深度50公里，屬淺層地震。<br />\n<br />\n現時，當局未有發出海嘯警告，亦未傳出任何傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n本港天文台則錄得今次地震強度為5.8級。"},{"pid":"7b5886b4fcbbc4d1a4a9433c1676870509630f03","tid":962432,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:23:46.000Z","msg":"果到係咪大雪緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c32070726d6070024471a6d942137708ffd934","tid":962432,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"雪崩咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ea073e783024379fcc82131eaadd0e8aa3a876","tid":962432,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c32070726d6070024471a6d942137708ffd934","tid":962432,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"雪崩咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:33:53.000Z","msg":"應該對居民地方影響唔大"}]}